## 開発用セットアップ
プロジェクト構築後に、以下の手順で実行環境を構築します

```bash
cd <your-project-name>

# Install dependencies
pnpm install

# Run formatting and linting (automatically runs on commit)
pnpm run lint
pnpm run lint:fix
pnpm run format
pnpm run format:fix

# Run typecheck
pnpm run typecheck
pnpm run typecheck:full

# Run lint and format before commit
pnpm run prepare

# Run dev
pnpm run dev

# Run build
pnpm run build

# Run Production
pnpm start

```

